description:
The Elden Ring: Deluxe Edition is a digital special edition of Elden Ring that offers additional content alongside the base game. This edition includes:

- Digital copy of the game: The full game available for download;
- Digital Artbook: A detailed artbook that showcases concept art, character designs, landscapes, and other visual elements from the game, providing insight into the development and artistic direction of Elden Ring;
- Original Soundtrack: A digital version of the game's soundtrack.

The Elden Ring: Launch Edition is a special edition of Elden Ring that was available at the game's release. This edition includes several physical and digital items aimed at enhancing the experience for early adopters. It includes:

- Physical copy of the game;
- Exclusive SteelBook Case: A collectible metal case featuring unique artwork.
- Art Cards: A set of 3 exclusive art cards depicting scenes or characters from the game.
- Woven Patch: A patch featuring a significant symbol from Elden Ring;
- Stickers: A set of stickers with designs related to the game;
- Poster: An exclusive poster showcasing artwork from the game.

The Elden Ring: Collector's Edition is a special game edition that includes the following physical and digital bonuses for fans and collectors:

- Physical copy of the game;
- SteelBook Case: A collectable metal case featuring unique artwork;
- Statue of Malenia – Blade of Miquella: A finely detailed 9-inch statue of one of the game’s key characters;
- Exclusive Artbook: A 40-page hardcover artbook that provides a deeper look into the visual design and world-building of Elden Ring;
- Digital Soundtrack: A digital copy of the game's atmospheric and epic music score.
